node.text:
Marine scientists have spotted a yellow sea sponge and pink sea star hanging out together in real life‼️ 

According to DailyMail, Christopher Mah, a scientist with the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), shared his findings on Twitter, joking: 'I normally avoid these refs... but WOW. REAL LIFE SpongeBob and Patrick!'
